"lwekhusi, iqwalaselwe kakhulu kwaye akukho:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:187
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can use the <link linkend=\"menu-settings\"><guimenu>Settings</guimenu></"
