"guiicon> iqhosha okanye iMenubar <menuchoice><guimenu>Izixhobo</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Fumana ifayile...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> ukhetho. "
"Oku kuzakulungisa isicelo somfumani wefayile &kfind; kwi &konqueror; window. "
