#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:1050
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Link To Location (URL)..."
msgid "Link to Location (URL)…"
msgstr "Dibanisa Kwi Ndawo (URL)..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1051
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This lets you create an icon to open &konqueror; at a particular folder or "
"web page. As with <guimenuitem>Link To Application…</guimenuitem> you can "
"make the application icon appear on your desktop by creating the link in "
"your <filename>~/Desktop</filename> folder or going to the "
"<guisubmenu>Create New…</guisubmenu> sub menu by right clicking on a free "
"area of the desktop."
msgstr ""
"Oku kukuvumela wenze i icon ukuvula i &konqueror; kulawulo oluthile okanye "
"iphepha le web. Njenge <guimenuitem>Dibanisa kwi Sicelo...</guimenuitem> "
"ungenza i icon yesicelo ivele kwi desktop yakho ngokwenza ikhonkco kwi "
"<filename>~/Desktop</filename> ulawulo okanye yiya kwi <guisubmenu>Yenza "
"Entsha...</guisubmenu> imenu esezantsi ngokunqakraza kwi ariya "
"ekhululekileyo ye desktop. Xa usenza yona kuqala okubhaliweyo okuboniswayo "
"nge icon izakubangemendo opheleleyo okanye i &URL;, ungayitshintsha "
"ngokunqakraza kwi icon, ukhethe <guimenuitem>Iimpahla... </guimenuitem> "
"nokungenisa okubhaliweyo okukhethwayo kwi <guilabel>Ngokubanzi </guilabel> "
"iphepha lesithuba."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:1060
#, no-c-format
msgid "Link to File or Directory…"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1061
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create a symbolic link for local files or folder."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:1065
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Link To Application..."
msgid "Link to Application…"
msgstr "Dibanisa Kwi Sicelo..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1066
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option is most useful if you want to create an icon that will open a "
"particular application. It opens a dialog box with several tabbed pages. The "
"first, <guilabel>General</guilabel>, is where you choose an icon and the "
"text that will appear with it. The second page, <guilabel>Permissions</"
"guilabel>, lets you select who can use or modify the icon. In the "
"<guilabel>Application</guilabel> page you must enter the <guilabel>Command</"
"guilabel> that will run the application, for example, <userinput>kwrite</"
"userinput> to start up the &kwrite; text editor. <userinput>kwrite /home/pam/"
"todo.txt</userinput> would open the file <filename>/home/pam/todo.txt</"
"filename> in &kwrite;. Advanced options such as the file types which the "
"application can open are also available from this page."
msgstr ""
"Olu khetho luluncedo kakhulu ukuba ufuna ukwenza i icon ezakuvula isicelo "
"esithile. Ivula ibhokisi yencoko yababini ngamaphepha amane anesithuba. "
"Eyokuqala, <guilabel>Ngokubanzi</guilabel>, kulapho ukhetha khona i Icon "
"nokubhaliweyo okuvela ngayo. Iphepha lesibini, <guilabel>Iimvume</guilabel>, "
"ikuvumela ukhethe ukuba ngubani onokusebenzisa okanye aguqule kancinane i "
"icon. Kwi <guilabel>Phumeza</guilabel> iphepha ekufuneka ungenise kulo "
"umyalelo ozakusebenza isicelo, umzekelo <userinput>kedit</userinput> ukuqala "
"i &kedit; umhleli wokubhaliweyo. <userinput>kedit /home/pam/todo.txt</"
"userinput> uzakuvula ifayile <filename>/home/pam/todo.txt</filename> in "
"&kedit;. Ungashiya ngokubanzi i <guilabel>Isicelo</guilabel> iphepha "
"lingenanto."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1078
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To make the application icon appear on your desktop, create the link in your "
"<filename class=\"directory\">~/Desktop</filename> folder (this may be "
"called something slightly different depending on how &kde; was installed on "
"your system) or get to the <guisubmenu>Create New…</guisubmenu> sub menu by "
"<mousebutton>right</mousebutton> clicking on a free area of the desktop "
"instead of within &konqueror;’s window."
msgstr ""
"Ukwenza i icon yesicelo ivele kweyakho idesktop, yenza ikhonkco kweyakho "
"<filename class=\"directory\">~/Desktop</filename> ulawulo okanye yiya ku "
"<guisubmenu>Yenza Entsha... </guisubmenu> imenu esezantsi nge "
"<mousebutton>ekunene</mousebutton> nqakraza kwi ariya ekhululekileyo ye "
"desktop."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1085
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have a lot of specialized application links and don’t want to clutter "
"up the desktop, then why not create them in your Applications folder. You "
"can get there in &konqueror; by choosing <menuchoice><guimenu>Go</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Applications</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Then create a single "
"icon on your desktop to open your Applications folder, which is usually in "
"<filename class=\"directory\">~/.local/share/applications</filename>."
msgstr ""
"Ukuba unamakhonkco amaninzi esicelo kwaye awufuni ukungcolisa idesktop, "
"ngoku kutheni ungazenzi kulawulo lwakho lweSicelo. Ungaya apho kwi "
"&konqueror; ngokukhetha i <menuchoice><guimenu>Hamba</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Izicelo</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Ngoku yenza eyodwa i icon "
"kwi desktop yakho ukuvula ulawulo lwakho lweZicelo, ngesiqhelo ekwi "
"<filename class=\"directory\">~/.kde/share/applink</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1091
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To put an application link icon into the panel, first create it in the "
"Applications folder then drag the icon onto a clear area of the panel."
msgstr ""
"Ukubeka i icon yekhonkco lesicelo kwiqela lenjongo, yenze kuqala kulawulo "
"lweZicelo ngoku tsala i icon kwi ariya ecacileyo yeqela lenjongo ethile."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1100
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "Changing Names and Permissions"
msgstr "Itshintsha Igama ne Mvume"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1102
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The two easiest ways to change the name of a file or folder is to either "
"<mousebutton>right</mousebutton> click on it and select <guimenuitem>Rename</"
"guimenuitem>, or select the file or folder and then press the <keycap>F2</"
"keycap> key."
msgstr ""
"Indlela elula ukutshintsha igama lefayile okanye ulawulo ku "
"<mousebutton>ekunene</mousebutton> nqakraza kuyo kwaye khetha i "
"<guimenuitem>Nika igama kwakhona</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1106
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To change the name or permissions of a file or folder <mousebutton>right</"
"mousebutton> click on its name or icon and select the "
"<guimenuitem>Properties</guimenuitem> item, or if you have <quote>selected</"
"quote> the file or folder, then you can use the Menubar "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Properties</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>Return</keycap></"
"keycombo>) option."
msgstr ""
"Okanye, ukutshintsha igama okanye iimvume zefayile okanye ulawulo "
"<mousebutton>ekunene</mousebutton> nqakraza kwigama layo okanye i icon kwaye "
"khetha i <guimenuitem>Iimpahla...</guimenuitem>umba. Okanye, ukuba une "
"<quote>ekhethiweyo</quote> ifayile okanye ulawulo, ngoku ungasebenzisa "
"iMenubar <menuchoice><guimenu>Hlela</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Iimpahla</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> ukhetho."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1113
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "This will bring up the Properties dialog box with several tabbed pages:"
msgstr ""
"Oku kuzakuzisa ibhokisi yencoko yababini yeeMpahla enezithuba ezimbini:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1117
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>General</guilabel>, which gives you some information about the "
"item and lets you change its name and, for a folder, the associated icon."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Ngokubanzi</guilabel>, esikunika ulwazi malunga nomba kwaye "
"ikuvumela utshintshe igama layo nelo lawulo, eyayama nisiweyo i icon."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1120
