msgid ""
"Printing a copy of the page you are viewing is easily done with the Menubar "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Print…</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> or <guimenuitem>Print Frame</guimenuitem> option or with the "
"Toolbar <guiicon>Print</guiicon> button."
msgstr ""
"Ukushicilela ukhuphelo lwephepha oliboniselayo kwenzeka lula nge Menubar "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Indawo</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Shicilela...</"
"guimenuitem></ menuchoice> okanye <guimenuitem>Shicilela Isakhelo</"
"guimenuitem> ukhetho, okanye nge ngebar yeSixhobo <guiicon>Shicilela</"
"guiicon> iqhosha."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1478
#, no-c-format
msgid "&FTP;"
msgstr "&FTP;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1480
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&FTP;, or File Transfer Protocol, is one of the the earliest, and still "
#| "perhaps the best, way of transferring files between computers over the "
#| "Internet."
msgid ""
"&FTP;, or File Transfer Protocol, is one of the earliest, and still perhaps "
"the best, way of transferring files between computers over the Internet."
msgstr ""
"&FTP;, okanye iProtocol Yonikezelo yeFayile, yenye yeziphambili, kwaye "
"mhlawumbi isengcono, indlela yokunikezela iifayile phakathi kwee computer "
"ngapha kwi Internet."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1484
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With &FTP; you can see files and folders on the distant computer just as if "
"they were on your own system, download them onto your computer using "
"&konqueror;’s normal <guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem> and <guimenuitem>Paste</"
"guimenuitem> or Drag’n Drop methods and, if allowed, upload files from your "
"machine to the other computer’s filesystem. To try it, type the &URL;"
msgstr ""
"Ngge &FTP; ungabona iifayile nabalawuli kwi computer esendaweni njengokuba "
"bezinjalo kwindlela yakho, zilayishe ezantsi kwi computer yakho usebenzisa i "
"&konqueror; eqhelekileyo <guimenuitem>Khuphela</guimenuitem> ne "
"<guimenuitem>Cola</guimenuitem> okanye iindlela zo Tsala no Lahla kwaye; "
"ukuba kuyavumeleka; layisha phezulu iifayile kwimatshini yakho ukuya kwenye "
"indlela yefayile yecomputer. Ukuyizama, chwetheza i <acronym>URL</acronym>"

#. Tag: screen
#: index.docbook:1491
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>ftp://ftp.l10n.kde.org</userinput>"
msgstr "ftp://ftp.kde.org/pub/kde"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1493
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"into the Location Toolbar and press <keysym>Enter</keysym>. As long as you "
"are connected to the Internet, you should end up seeing the <filename class="
"\"directory\">ftp</filename> folder of the l10n server."
msgstr ""
"kwibar yeNdawo kwaye cinezela <keycap>Ngena</keycap>. Nje ukuba udityanisiwe "
"kwi Internet, kwaye nje ukuba i &kde;'s &FTP; inxuwa alixakekanga kakhulu, "
"ungaphela ubona i <filename class=\"directory\">/pub/kde</filename> ulawulo "
"kwi ftp.kde.org"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1497
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Although, strictly speaking, &FTP; &URL;s should be entered starting with "
"<userinput>ftp://</userinput> and <acronym>WWW </acronym> &URL;s starting "
"with <userinput>http://</userinput> &konqueror; is usually smart enough to "
"figure out what is meant, and insert these characters for you if you leave "
"them out."
msgstr ""
"Noxa, uthetha ngokuphandle, &FTP; <acronym>URL</acronym>'s inokungeniswa "
"uqala nge <userinput>ftp://</userinput> ne <abbrev>WWW</abbrev> "
"<acronym>URL</acronym>s iqala nge <userinput>http://</userinput> &konqueror; "
"iqhele ukubukeka ngokwaneleyo ukuqwalasela okuthethwayo, kwaye faka aba "
"basebenzi bakho ukuba ubashiya ngaphandle."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1503
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you access an &FTP; site it will usually need some form of username and "
"password from you. To simplify things, most &FTP; sites that offer files for "
"free downloading will accept the word <systemitem class=\"username\"> "
"anonymous</systemitem> as a username and your email address as a password, "
"and to make your life even easier &konqueror; will automatically supply "
"these without troubling you."
msgstr ""
"Xa unikeza i &FTP; inxuwa liqhele ukufuna enye indlela yegama lomsebenzisi "
"negama eligqithisiweyo kuwe. Ukucacisa izinto, ezininzi i &FTP; amanxuwa "
