#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1650
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using Bookmarks"
msgstr "Usebenzisa Amanqaku encwadi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1652
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Although you can use &konqueror;’s bookmarks to record the locations of your "
"own files and folders, they are most useful when you are surfing the Web, "
"letting you build up a list of useful sites."
msgstr ""
"Noxa ungasebenzisa i &konqueror; amanqaku encwadi ukushicilela iindawo "
"yeefayile zakho nabalawuli, baluncedo kakhulu xa ukhangela i Web, ikuvumela "
"wakhe uluhlu lwamanxuwa aluncedo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1656
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To open the <guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu> menu <mousebutton>left</"
"mousebutton> click on the <guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu> menu. Once the list "
"is visible, you can navigate through it with the arrow keys or with your "
"mouse, then press <keysym>Enter</keysym> or <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> "
"click to visit the selected location."
msgstr ""
"Ukuvula i <guimenu>Amanqaku encwadi</guimenu> lahla-phantsi uluhlu onokuli "
"noba <mousebutton>ekhohlo</mousebutton> nqakraza kwi Menubar "
"<guimenu>Amanqaku encwadi</guimenu> umba, okanye sebenzisa i <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\"><keycap>Alt</keycap><keycap>B</keycap></keycombo> hotkey. "
"Xa uluhlu lubonakala, ungalawula ngapha kwayo ngezitshixo zetolo okanye "
"imouse yakho, ngoku cinezela <keycap>Ngena</keycap> okanye &LMB; nqakraza "
"ukundwendwela indawo ekhethiweyo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1662
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To add a new item to the list use <menuchoice><guimenu>Bookmarks </"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Add Bookmark</guimenuitem></menuchoice> or <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>B</keycap></keycombo> or <mousebutton>right</"
"mousebutton> click on a clear space in the web page or folder view and "
"select <guimenuitem>Bookmark this Page</guimenuitem> from the pop up menu."
msgstr ""
"Ukudibanisa umba omtsha kuluhlu sebenzisa iMenubar <link linkend=\"menu-"
"bookmarks\"><menuchoice><guimenu>Amanqaku encwadi</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Dibanisa Inqaku lencwadi</guimenuitem></menuchoice></link> umba "
"okanye <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>Ctrl</keycap><keycap>B</keycap></"
"keycombo> okanye <mousebutton>ekunene</mousebutton> nqakraza kwaye ukhethe i "
"<guimenuitem>Dibanisa kuManqaku encwadi</guimenuitem> xa ubonisela ulawulo "
"olufunekayo okanye iphepha le web."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1669
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu> list can contain subfolders containing "
"other bookmarks, you can create these with <menuchoice><guimenu>Bookmarks </"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>New Bookmark Folder…</guimenuitem></menuchoice> To add "
"a bookmark into a subfolder rather than into the main Bookmark list, select "
"the folder from within the <guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu> list and use the "
"<guimenuitem>Add Bookmark</guimenuitem> item in that folder."
msgstr ""
"Ukudibanisa inqaku lencwadi kwincwadi eneenkcukacha-esezantsi kunoluhlu "
"olungundoqo lenqaku lencwadi, khetha lo ncwadi eneenkcukacha kwi "
"<guimenu>Amanqaku encwadi</guimenu> menu kwaye sebenzisa i "
"<guimenuitem>Dibanisa Inqaku lencwadi</guimenuitem> umba kulo ncwadi "
"eneenkcukacha."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1679
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you enter <userinput>bookmarks:</userinput> in the location bar the "
"bookmarks home page with an overview of all bookmarks and folders is shown."
msgstr ""

