"apply the view properties to the <guilabel>Current folder</guilabel>. Doing "
"this creates a <filename>.directory</filename> file in that folder to hold "
"the folder <guimenu>View</guimenu> settings. Use this dialog again to remove "
"the folder specific settings (or just delete the <filename>.directory</"
"filename> file)."
msgstr ""
"Kodwa ungakhankanya eyahlukileyo i <guimenu>Imboniselo</guimenu> "
"izicwangciso zemenu zalo naluphi na ulawulo olulodwa. Ukwenza oku khangela i "
"<guimenuitem>Iimpahla zeMboniselo ziGcinwa kuLawulo</guimenuitem> ibhokisi "
"kwi <guimenu>Izicwangciso</guimenu> menu, tshintsha i <guimenu>Imboniselo</"
"guimenu> izicwangciso naphi na ofuna khona kwaye sukukhangela i "
"<guimenuitem>Iimpahla yeMboniselo igcinwa kuLawulo</guimenuitem> ibhokisi. "
"Ukwenza oku kwenza i <filename>.ulawulo</filename> ifayile kolo lawulo "
"ukubamba ulawulo <guimenu>Imboniselo</guimenu> izicwangciso. Sebenzisa i "
"<menuchoice><guimenu> Izicwangciso</guimenu><guimenuitem>Susa Iimpahla "
"zoLawulo</guimenuitem></menuchoice> ukhetho ukususa izicwangciso zolawulo "
"oluthile (okanye cima nje i <filename>.directory</filename> file)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1925
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"One nice use of this feature is if you have a folder full of pictures, you "
"can set that particular folder to display thumbnails of the pictures (by "
"choosing the <menuchoice><guisubmenu>View Mode</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Icons</guimenuitem></menuchoice> and <guimenuitem>Preview</"
