msgstr "Imibuzo Neempendulo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3513
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I run &konqueror; from another window manager?"
msgstr "Ndingayisebenzisa i &konqueror; komnye umphathi we window?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3516
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Just install &Qt;, &kde-frameworks; and &konqueror;, and from your favorite "
"window manager, launch &konqueror;. It should work just fine, but if it "
"doesn’t (&kde; developers don’t test that case often), report it to <ulink "
"url=\"https://bugs.kde.org\">https://bugs.kde.org</ulink> and try running "
"<application>kdeinit</application> before running &konqueror;; it usually "
"helps."
msgstr ""
"Faka nje &Qt;, kdelibs ne kdebase, kwaye ukusuka kumphathi omthandayo we "
"window , yazisa nje i &konqueror;. Inokusebenza nje kakuhle, kodwa ukuba "
"ayenzeki (&kde; ababhekisi phambili abawuvavanyi lo mzekelo rhoqo), yixele "
"kwi <ulink url=\"http://bugs.kde.org\">http://bugs.kde.org</ulink> kwaye "
"zama ukusebenza <application>kdeinit</application> phambi kokusebenzisa i "
"&konqueror;, iqhele ukunceda."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3525
#, no-c-format
msgid "Where does &konqueror; keep all its configuration data?"
msgstr "Iyigcina phi i &konqueror; yonke idata yayo yoqwalaselo?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3527
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Generally in the <filename class=\"directory\">qtpaths --paths "
"GenericDataLocation</filename> folder (this may be <filename>~/.local/share</"
"filename> on your system, depending on how &konqueror; was installed). Don’t "
"alter these files unless you really know what you are doing."
msgstr ""
"Ngokubanzi kwi <filename>~/.kde</filename> abalawuli. (inokuba inga yi "
"<filename>~/.kde3 </filename> kwindlela yakho, ixhomekeke kwindlela i &kde; "
"3 efakelelwe ngayo). Sukuzihambisa kunye ezifayile ngaphandle kokuba uyazi "
"ngenene okwenzayo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3534
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Your bookmarks are held in <filename class=\"directory\">~/.kde/share/"
#| "apps/konqueror/bookmarks.xml</filename>"
msgid ""
"Your bookmarks are held in <filename class=\"directory\">konqueror/bookmarks."
"xml</filename>"
msgstr ""
"Amanqaku wakho encwadi abanjwa kwi <filename class=\"directory\">~/.kde/"
"share/apps/konqueror/bookmarks.xml</filename>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3536
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Cookies are held in <filename class=\"directory\">~/.kde/share/apps/"
#| "kcookiejar/cookies</filename>"
msgid ""
"Cookies are held in <filename class=\"directory\">kcookiejar/cookies</"
"filename>"
msgstr ""
"Cookies zibanjwa kwi <filename class=\"directory\">~/.kde/share/apps/"
"kcookiejar/cookies</filename>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3539
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Your history, as used for the auto-completion feature, is in <filename>~/."
#| "kde/share/config/konq_history</filename>"
msgid ""
"Your history, as used for the auto-completion feature, is in "
"<filename>konq_history</filename> in the folder <filename class=\"directory"
"\">qtpaths --paths GenericConfigLocation</filename>."
msgstr ""
"Imbali yakho, njengoko isetyenziswa kugqibo-oluzenzekelayo lomsebenzi, ikwi "
"<filename>~/.kde/share/config/konq_history</filename>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3541
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the folder <filename class=\"directory\">qtpaths --paths "
"GenericConfigLocation</filename> the file <filename>konquerorrc</filename> "
"holds a whole lot of general configuration settings."
msgstr ""
"Kulawulo <filename class=\"directory\">~/.kde/share/config/</filename> "
"iifayile <filename>konqiconviewrc</filename>, <filename>konqlistviewrc</"
"filename> ne <filename>konquerorrc</filename> ibamba zonke izicwangciso "
"zoqwalaselo ngokubanzi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3546
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The folder <filename class=\"directory\">kio_http/</filename> in <filename "
"class=\"directory\">qtpaths --paths GenericCacheLocation</filename> contains "
"the browser cache."
msgstr ""
"Ulawulo <filename class=\"directory\">~/.kde/share/cache/http/</filename> "
"iqulathe indawo yokugcina yomkhangeli zincwadi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3551
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Any folder specific view settings are put into <literal role=\"extension\">."
"directory</literal> files in the individual folders."
msgstr ""
"Naziphi izicwangciso zemboniselo ezithile zolawulo zibekwa kwi <literal role="
"\"extension\">.ulawulo</literal> iifayile kubalawuli ababodwa."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3557
#, no-c-format
msgid "How do I clear out the history file?"
msgstr "Ndiyicacisa njani ifayile yembali (ibankulu noko)?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3558
#, no-c-format
msgid "There are two <quote>histories</quote>:"
msgstr "Zimbini <quote>imbali</quote>:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3560
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"One is used for text completion in the Location Toolbar text entry box. To "
"clear this <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> click on the text entry box and "
"select <guimenuitem>Clear History </guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"Enye isebenziswa ukugqibezela okubaliweyo Kwindawo ekuyo ibhari yesixhobo "
"kwibhokisi yokungenisa. Ukucima oku <mousebutton>ekunene</mousebutton>  "
"nqakraza kuyo kwaye khetha i <guimenuitem></guimenuitem>.Imixholo Engananto "
"</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3565
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The other is the log of visited locations. Select the History page in the "
#| "Navigation Panel, <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> click on an entry and "
#| "choose <guimenuitem>Remove Entry</guimenuitem> to remove just that entry "
#| "or <guimenuitem>Clear History</guimenuitem> to delete all entries."
msgid ""
"The other is the log of visited locations. Select <guimenuitem>Show History</"
"guimenuitem> in the menu <guimenu>Go</guimenu> and <mousebutton>right</"
"mousebutton> click on an entry and choose <guimenuitem>Remove Entry</"
"guimenuitem> (&Del;) to remove just that entry or <guimenuitem>Clear "
"History</guimenuitem> to delete all entries."
msgstr "Enye"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3571
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also use the application &sweeper; from the kdeutils module which "
"allows you to clean up cookies, favicons, web history and cache, form "
"completion entries and cache policies of visited websites."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3578
#, no-c-format
msgid "How do I enable, disable or clear the browser cache?"
msgstr ""
"Ndiyenza njani, khubaza okanye cacisa indawo yokugcina yomkhangeli zincwadi?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3580
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you select <menuchoice><guimenu>Web Browsing</guimenu><guimenuitem>Cache</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> in the dialog launched by selecting "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Konqueror…</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, you will be presented with a dialog box that lets "
"you disable the cache, clear it or set its size, and change the caching "
"policy."
msgstr ""
"Ukuba ukhetha <menuchoice><guisubmenu>Ezikhethwayo</guisubmenu><guisubmenu> "
"Ukhangelo lwe Web</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>i Cache</menuchoice> kwi K menu "
"uzakufumana ibhokisi yencoko yababini ekuvumelayo ukuba ukhubaze i cache, "
"yicime okanye cwangcisa ubungakanani bayo, utshintshe inkqubo ye cache."

